HEADWORD: Creaking
<hw>Creak"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A harsh grating or squeaking
sound, or the act of making such a sound.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Start not at the <qex>creaking</qex> of the door.</q>
<rj><qau>Longfellow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>creaky</ent>⟦br⟧
